title: Pair sought in Uptown armed robbery
text:
NEW ORLEANS (WVUE) - Police are searching for two men in connection to an early morning armed robbery uptown.
The victim was approached by two unknown black males in the 5300 block of St. Charles Ave around 1:18 a.m. on Oct 17.
The suspects pulled out a silver revolver and demanded the victimâ€™s property. The victims complied and the two armed men fled with an ID, credit card and $400 in cash.
Police encourage anyone with information to call CRIMESTOPPERS at 504-822-1111.
